somewhere-- in your case,

00:03:23.430 --> 00:03:27.650
maybe in Europe, or the Middle
Eastern and North Africa.

00:03:27.650 --> 00:03:29.120
And then from
there, you're going

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:30.430
to look for another market.

00:03:30.430 --> 00:03:32.390
You look for a market
that's somewhat similar.

00:03:32.390 --> 00:03:34.000
Maybe another Western country.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.805
Maybe a market that has
similar user patterns.

00:03:37.805 --> 00:03:39.180
And then from
there, you're going

00:03:39.180 --> 00:03:40.596
to go to another
market that maybe

00:03:40.596 --> 00:03:42.870
is even more
different than yours.

00:03:42.870 --> 00:03:45.710
And all of sudden, the amazing
thing is, all of a sudden,

00:03:45.710 --> 00:03:47.890
