sales from outside the US.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.740
It was like management
changes, and the way

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:02.940
the company does
things just change.

00:04:02.940 --> 00:04:07.042
And today, it happens so
quickly that a lot of developers

00:04:07.042 --> 00:04:08.500
actually don't
change their mindset

00:04:08.500 --> 00:04:10.637
as they become
global developers.

00:04:10.637 --> 00:04:12.470
And so what I want to
talk to you about next

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:14.770
is how do you actually
change your mindset, what

00:04:14.770 --> 00:04:17.910
are things you can do as
